go."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The company was a startup, so the pace was actually faster than that of traditional companies."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"However, my family member's illness began to affect my ability to focus daily."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"the-conflict-between-family-and-work"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"className":["text-lg","font-bold"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Conflict Between Family and Work"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Due to my family member's physical weakness"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I had to take on all household chores and frequently take them to the doctor."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The treatments were not showing significant improvement."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"During work, I often found myself thinking about what else I could do to help my family member recover more quickly."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"My mentor was highly capable and worked at a fast pace."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"As a result, the decline in my work quality quickly became apparent to my mentor."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"making-the-decision"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"className":["text-lg","font-bold"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Making the Decision"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Faced with this situation, I ultimately decided to resign"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To focus on caring for my family"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Once my family member's health stabilizes, I will consider my next steps."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I understand that work can be found again, but if I miss this chance to care for my family member's health, I might regret not making this decision."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"the-significance-of-resignation"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"className":["text-lg","font-bold"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Significance of Resignation"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This decision to resign is not only for my family but also for myself to take a much-needed break and work on the blog I've always wanted to complete."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In the five years since I started working, I've always transitioned seamlessly between jobs, never having a true gap year."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Now, this opportunity, born out of my family member's illness, allows me to recharge and better prepare for the next steps in my life."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The right decisions are always the hardest to make. But they must be made in order to live the life you deserve."}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"the-turn-